content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1151.16 - Coin-operated doors and turnstiles

State Regulations

No person shall pass through, over, under or around a
coin-operated door or turnstile at any transportation facility without having
deposited the appropriate coin in such door or turnstile. Notes
